# TanStack Start

- Use file-based routes and keep route modules small.
- Do not read `process.env.*` in route loaders or components.
- Server-only behavior belongs in server functions or server-only modules.
- Never hand-edit `routeTree.gen.ts`; let TanStack tooling generate it.
- Prefer TanStack Query/Form/Table/Store for their respective concerns.
